The class is limited to returning 1x1 or single value result sets, but it is a result set nonetheless. Here&#39;s how you would implement it in your case.

    private boolean checkUser(String email, String password) {
        sqLiteDatabase = new MyOpenHelper(this).getWritableDatabase();
        
