Before calls to PDFBox are made it is highly recommended to initialize the library&#39;s resource loader. Add the following line before calling PDFBox methods:

    PDFBoxResourceLoader.init(getApplicationContext());

So edit your code 

    .....
    @RequiresApi(Build.VERSION_CODES.LOLLIPOP)
    override fun onCreate(savedInstanceState: Bundle?) {
    super.onCreate(savedInstanceState)
       setContentView(R.layout.activity_main)

       PDFBoxResourceLoader.init(getApplicationContext());//call this
       var file1:Button = findViewById(R.id.file1);
       file1.setOnClickListener(::chooseFile)
    }

